Pure Prompt
Install and Verify:
 
 
npm install --global pure-prompt
echo 'autoload -U promptinit; promptinit; prompt pure' >> ~/.zshrc
source ~/.zshrc
pure --version
Disable and Remove:
 
 
sed -i '/autoload -U promptinit; promptinit; prompt pure/d' ~/.zshrc
npm uninstall --global pure-prompt
source ~/.zshrc
